Read more

Ergonomic Design

The form of T10 completely suits the curve of inside contour of ear.

With spherical tender silicone eartips, it may possibly provide extra sporting stability and luxury when in use.

Whether you’ re working or leaping, the earbuds will keep in ear securely.

Advanced Bluetooth 5.0 Technology

Support HSP, HFP, A2DP, AVRCP. Provides in-call stereo sound.

Greatly enhance the transmission pace and offering you with a low-latency listening expertise.

The 8.0 MM Drive Area is 1.77 Times than the Normal Drive Area.

TOZO acoustic consultants foucus on exact acoustic tuning and discover out the very best sound traits for human listening to sensitivity.

Accurately alter each element to attain an ideal steadiness of bass, midrange and treble.

TOZO T10 present highly effective bass( lowest 12Hz), mellow midrange, and clear treble(as much as 20kHz). Reappearing each element of the music vividly.

Read more

Both Earbuds and Charging Case are IPX8 Waterproof Protection

IPX8 Waterproof Nano-coating effectively protects the earbuds and charging case from the harm of the splash by sweat and raindrops.

Earbuds and case even may be washed by water and cleaning soap.

No want to fret once you put on it whereas working,snowboarding, and so on. (not for swimming)

One Step Pairing

Pick up 2 headsets from the charging case and they’ll join one another mechanically.

Then just one step simply enter cell phone’s Bluetooth setting and select “TOZO-T10” to pair the earbuds.

Note: If you unintentionally get just one earbud paired with cellphone, please strive “Reset” choices. (Pls refer “Reset” particulars in handbook)

Upgraded Faster Wireless Charging

Enjoy quick charging, to totally cost the rechargerable case only one.5 hours by way of quick cost USB-C cable or lower than 2 hours by way of wi-fi charger.

Playtime lasts for over 6 hours from single cost and whole 30 hours with charging case.

The charging case is suitable with most of wi-fi chargers.

Note: Wireless charger not included.

[BLUETOOTH 5.0] Funktioner med den avancerade Bluetooth 5.0-tekniken, TOZO T10 öronsnäckor stöder HSP HFP A2DP AVRCP, som ger omedelbar ihopparning och stabil överföring utan avbrott.
[Enstegsparning] Ta helt enkelt ut två headset från laddningsfodralet, så kommer de att ansluta varandra automatiskt och sedan går bara ett steg in i Bluetooth-inställningen för mobiltelefonen för att para ihop öronsnäckorna.
[IPX8 vattentät] Öronproppar och laddningsfodral inre Nano-beläggning gör det möjligt att vattentäta i 1 meters djup i 30 minuter. Vattentät och svettbeständig senaste teknik kan effektivt förhindra skador på stänk av svett och regndroppar.
[Laddning på språng] Speltiden varar i över 6 timmar från enstaka laddning och totalt 30 timmar med laddningsväska. Njut av snabb laddning, för att helt ladda det laddningsbara fodralet endast 1,5 timmar by way of snabb laddning USB-C-kabel eller mindre än 2 timmar by way of trådlös laddare. Ger ett bekvämt laddningssätt utan några strängar.
